data.description:
***Welcome to best in luxury living!*** 3.125% Assumable loan***You Do need to be VA eligible to assume the loan***HIT A HOLE-IN-ONE WITH THIS GEM***Blackstone Country Club's Golf award-winning, (membership separate) 18-hole, par 72 championship, Private golf course designed by Jim Engh. ***Prime corner lot***in the guard gated community***No homes on 3 sides backs to desert. Close to the Country Club. Architecturally pleasing open floor plan, bathed in natural light, boasting modern wood-look tile flooring, high ceilings, fire sprinklers, plantation shutters, & modern light fixtures. Cook like a chef in the gourmet kitchen offering SS appliances, 6 burner gas cooktop, double ovens, walk- in pantry, exquisite cabinetry, tile backsplash, an island w/breakfast bar, & granite counters. The split owner's suite has a lavish bathroom featuring dual sinks, a generously sized Super shower with double  shower heads, & an ample walk-in closet. Beyond the beauty, the home is practical, with a dedicated mudroom & a spacious laundry room w/utility sinks & cabinet storage, soft water loop, garage has cabinets and electric car charging installed! The backyard highlights a covered patio with a Sun Shade that you'll love, a shimmering pool, a view fence backing to the desert with spectacular sunsets & astonishing mountain views & raised garden beds. Make this gem yours. Blackstone is a private, guard gated country club community featuring magnificent amenities Hacienda Clubhouse, extensive fitness center, resort-style pool with private cabanas, children's play area, tennis facilities, wine bar & casual and fine dining. Blackstone is close to Lake Pleasant which offers camping, boating, fishing, swimming, hiking, picnicking & wildlife
*Award winning Peoria School District*
